The layout file is written in the follwing way:

Line 1 :  <height of the grid> <width of the grid> <number of ghosts>
Next <<height of the grid>> lines : description of the grid
    walls : %
    food : .
    otherwise : whitespace
<x co-ordinate : line in which pacman is> <y co-ordinate :position in that line for pacman> 0
Next <<number of ghosts>> lines : description of the ghosts
<x co-ordinate : line in which ghost is> <y co-ordinate :position in that line for the ghost> <direction of the ghost>
    Direction 0 : no direction
    Direction 1 : East
    Direction 2 : West
    Direction 3 : North
    Direction 4 : South

